Section 10:

Mud News

Among some of the more helpful additions to the mud is a social worker
above the city surplus that will supply newbies with new gear if they are 
unlucky enough to lose bits of equipment.  Several other changes to mud
policy and code have also occurred due to the conversion from <h> 4.5 to
<h> 5.0.  Use the Mud's news function to hear about the most recent news
on the mud.  For more information use Help News.

